FBIS4-16602 "drsov075_u_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-075 Daily Report 18 Apr 1994 Latvia Sweden to Send Financial Aid to Develop Baltic Defenses Sweden to Send Financial Aid to Develop Baltic Defenses LD1804172694 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 0900 GMT 18 Apr 94 LD1804172694 Riga Radio Riga Network Latvian BFN [Text] The Swedish Government has decided to grant 1.4 million Swedish krona to create defense systems in the Baltic states. These funds will be used for consultations and training, and the acquisition of equipment and radars for both land and sea border protection. Experts from the Swedish defense forces have already become acquainted with the Baltic states' defense systems and have worked out proposals on how to improve them.
